{"tid":1167791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【亮劍了】中方就美艦再穿越台海提嚴正交涉","createTime":"2019-05-23T09:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T10:19:39.000Z","uid":11556,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"971b70d8e6b49e265dc7574fed2503dbf723aa32","tid":1167791,"uid":11556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:22:54.000Z","msg":"美國再派 2艘海軍艦艇穿越台灣海峽。在北京，外交部發言人陸慷表示，中方密切關注並全程掌握美國軍艦穿越台海的情況，有關部門已提出嚴正交涉。<br />\n<br />\n陸慷重申，中方敦促美方恪守一個中國原則和中美三個聯合公報，慎重妥善處理台灣問題，以免對中美關係造成消極影響。<br />\n<br />\n今次穿越台海的分別是美軍驅逐艦 &ldquo;普雷貝爾號&rdquo; 和補給艦 &ldquo;華特迪爾號&rdquo;，是繼上月 (4月) 底後，美軍再派艦艇穿越台海。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.tdm.com.mo/c_radio/news/news_img/radionews_2019-05-23_17-18-01_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tdm.com.mo%2Fc_radio%2Fnews%2Fnews_img%2Fradionews_2019-05-23_17-18-01_1.jpg&h=f4f69e70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5263a615c673629b9d780063cb294b6160d2eba","tid":1167791,"uid":254183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abecc5d159a4f0b0f6c1665a128180c2b56583e9","tid":1167791,"uid":77196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:25:20.000Z","msg":"咁撚把炮打撚沉佢囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7896e27ec14def46564d55538a5ab358038d9187","tid":1167791,"uid":18569,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:25:25.000Z","msg":"美帝：彈出彈入你咬我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70916b4f5d691fb66174fc538f6d1ea2799d7e0","tid":1167791,"uid":228963,"like":3,"dislike":39,"score":-36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c3a0b610b301e64a530a0ea57d2979c7753cc31","tid":1167791,"uid":31186,"like":1,"d